TitMainTitle: Men and women, including Carolyn Carter wearing long strand of pearls, seated next to smiling Al Carter, at center banquet table, Dr. R.E. Walden, Mrs. Walden, Dr. Earl Belle Smith, Mrs. Smith, Dr. LeMon, Mrs. LeMon, Dallas Lea, Mrs. Lea, Walter Tresville, Mrs. Tresville, and Cozetta Newring far left, in Anchorage for Kappa Alpha Psi's Kappa Karnival
